#
# Jeffrey's role in Node is *foundational
# parsing + TUI + cryptocurrency
# infrastructure*. He maintains canonical-
# status libraries across multiple
# verticals - one of the more prolific
# canonical-author contributors to the
# Node ecosystem before stepping back
# from active maintainership in the
