#
# Multi-axis canonical-Node author/org
# cohort extension (now spanning 26
# distinct individuals/orgs after R1552):
#   - + Christopher Jeffrey + Tony Brix
#     + markedjs org (markedjs/marked +
#     chjj/blessed; THIS AXIS; canonical
#     Node markdown parser + foundational
#     parsing + TUI infrastructure)
#
# Jeffrey + Brix joining the canonical-
# Node cohort at the *foundational
# parsing + reference-CLI co-maintainership*
# level continues the pattern documented
# at Axes 280 + 281 (Hildebrand + cbor-
# cli; websockets/ws + wscat). Both
# canonical libraries + reference CLIs
# are maintained by the same
