# library status: maintaining an end-user
# CLI alongside the library is a marker
# of canonical-status maturity.
#
# marked's CLI uses the marked library
# directly (via ESM import) for:
#   - Markdown parsing (Lexer + Parser
#     + Renderer pipeline)
#   - GFM extension handling
#   - Configuration loading + application
#   - Token AST output (when -t flag
